text:
Someone explained to me that with these UUP changes, we won’t see KB5027397 as a
separate KB like we did for Windows 10. 
It’s bundled inside of their UUP updates and the OS is just supposed to know
which bits to use. 
Windows 11, versions 23H2 x64 2023-10B 
Windows 11, versions 23H2 x64 2023-11B
